source.name: Resource Conservation and Recovery Act (RCRA) Widget
source.description: The Resource Conservation and Recovery Act (RCRA) widget reports facilities with hazardous waste activities for a user-specified area of interest as reported under Resource Conservation and Recovery Act requirements
